  "detailed_description": "<h1>ALASKAN ROAD TRUCKERS CONTENT!</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/849100/extras/0899819a5356b6b59ead0071bf62fa9d.avif?t=1770027117\" width=600 height=451 /></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Step into the boots of an Alaskan Trucker!</strong></h2>Live the thrill of a new kind of driving simulator and risk it all in the challenge to become an Alaskan trucking legend. Balance the risk vs reward of taking perilous routes to save time, perform roadside repairs on your rig and brave the dangerous conditions on foot in challenging survival-based gameplay.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/849100/extras/a503abf27b422c2fd6e06ddef2c21581.poster.avif?t=1770027117\" width=596 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/849100/extras/a503abf27b422c2fd6e06ddef2c21581.webm?t=1770027117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/849100/extras/a503abf27b422c2fd6e06ddef2c21581.mp4?t=1770027117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Drive</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Travel the wilds of Alaska in a sprawling map as you battle a dynamic weather system<br></li><li>Haul a range of cargo through the toughest conditions<br></li><li>Gear up and prepare for the journey ahead, with truck maintenance, emergency repairs and other challenges to contend with</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/849100/extras/aadd444b8e545707c74ac0992f7dfd33.poster.avif?t=1770027117\" width=596 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/849100/extras/aadd444b8e545707c74ac0992f7dfd33.webm?t=1770027117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/849100/extras/aadd444b8e545707c74ac0992f7dfd33.mp4?t=1770027117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Survive</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Stranded and low on funds for roadside assistance? Leave the safety of your cab and fix your truck, if you can brave the wintery conditions<br></li><li>Don’t just fuel your rig; contend with hunger, fatigue and body temperature to keep yourself healthy <br></li><li>Battle the elements with mudslides, avalanches, fallen trees and blizzards<br></li><li>Tackle three game modes; casual, standard and hardcore, for the most challenging experience</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/849100/extras/540556eb0cc083b530b8c94913634641.poster.avif?t=1770027117\" width=596 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/849100/extras/540556eb0cc083b530b8c94913634641.webm?t=1770027117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/849100/extras/540556eb0cc083b530b8c94913634641.mp4?t=1770027117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Thrive</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Make your mobile home your own - customise your truck and stand out from the crowd<br></li><li>Build your reputation, manage your HQ and be the master of your own destiny</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/849100/extras/428677e8365cba4aff86a21facdbc52b.poster.avif?t=1770027117\" width=596 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/849100/extras/428677e8365cba4aff86a21facdbc52b.webm?t=1770027117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/849100/extras/428677e8365cba4aff86a21facdbc52b.mp4?t=1770027117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Step into the boots of an Alaskan Trucker!</strong></h2>Live the thrill of a new kind of driving simulator and risk it all in the challenge to become an Alaskan trucking legend. Balance the risk vs reward of taking perilous routes to save time, perform roadside repairs on your rig and brave the dangerous conditions on foot in challenging survival-based gameplay.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/849100/extras/a503abf27b422c2fd6e06ddef2c21581.poster.avif?t=1770027117\" width=596 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/849100/extras/a503abf27b422c2fd6e06ddef2c21581.webm?t=1770027117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/849100/extras/a503abf27b422c2fd6e06ddef2c21581.mp4?t=1770027117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Drive</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Travel the wilds of Alaska in a sprawling map as you battle a dynamic weather system<br></li><li>Haul a range of cargo through the toughest conditions<br></li><li>Gear up and prepare for the journey ahead, with truck maintenance, emergency repairs and other challenges to contend with</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/849100/extras/aadd444b8e545707c74ac0992f7dfd33.poster.avif?t=1770027117\" width=596 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/849100/extras/aadd444b8e545707c74ac0992f7dfd33.webm?t=1770027117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/849100/extras/aadd444b8e545707c74ac0992f7dfd33.mp4?t=1770027117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Survive</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Stranded and low on funds for roadside assistance? Leave the safety of your cab and fix your truck, if you can brave the wintery conditions<br></li><li>Don’t just fuel your rig; contend with hunger, fatigue and body temperature to keep yourself healthy <br></li><li>Battle the elements with mudslides, avalanches, fallen trees and blizzards<br></li><li>Tackle three game modes; casual, standard and hardcore, for the most challenging experience</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/849100/extras/540556eb0cc083b530b8c94913634641.poster.avif?t=1770027117\" width=596 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/849100/extras/540556eb0cc083b530b8c94913634641.webm?t=1770027117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/849100/extras/540556eb0cc083b530b8c94913634641.mp4?t=1770027117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Thrive</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Make your mobile home your own - customise your truck and stand out from the crowd<br></li><li>Build your reputation, manage your HQ and be the master of your own destiny</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/849100/extras/428677e8365cba4aff86a21facdbc52b.poster.avif?t=1770027117\" width=596 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/849100/extras/428677e8365cba4aff86a21facdbc52b.webm?t=1770027117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/849100/extras/428677e8365cba4aff86a21facdbc52b.mp4?t=1770027117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
